  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_dentist_with_enhanced_skills">Dentist with Enhanced Skills</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_general_dental_practitioner">GENERAL DENTAL PRACTITIONER</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/primary-care/dentistry/dentistry-publications/#standards"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Dental publications</xref>
 defines complexity levels that reflect the competency required to deliver care of each complexity.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_dentist_with_enhanced_skills">Dentist with Enhanced Skills</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_dentist_with_enhanced_skills">DES</xref>) can be accredited as a Performer of Level 2 Complexity Care.        </p>
  </div>
